    "course_name": "Technology Diffusion, Leadership, and Change",
    "dept": "EDUC",
    "num": "511",
    "desc": "Prereq: Admission to graduate study, EDUC 501 or equivalent and EDUC 505 or equivalent\nPrinciples and practices of technology diffusion, leadership and school change. Coursework focuses on technology diffusion broadly and implications on educational contexts. Leadership frameworks and strategies for professional development and organizational change are examined, as well as new literacy practices, critical theory, and current debates in the field.\n",
