    "dept": "GERON",
    "num": "466",
    "desc": "Prereq: 9 credits in core courses for the gerontology minor and approval of the gerontology undergraduate coordinator\nPrepracticum training for students planning a gerontology practicum. Exploration of possible agencies for the practicum, in-depth study of a selected agency, and development of goals and objectives for the practicum.\n",
